      "text": "🧠 Memory that matters: OverMind-MCP gives each AI agent 4096D isolated memory via PostgreSQL + pgvector\n\nPrivate context. Shared knowledge base.\n\nnpm install -g overmind-mcp\n\nhttps://t.co/uLcS3lZjaQ\n\n#AI #Memory #PostgreSQL",
      "id": "2053111050287890637",
