      "author_id": "2030343281637572608",
      "created_at": "2026-05-09T13:44:00.000Z",
      "text": "memory in an AI agent isn't just context\n\nit's a governed data surface\n\nwhat the agent should know. what it shouldn't. what gets retained. who can change it.\n\ntreat it like an opaque implementation detail and you'll regret it later",
      "id": "2053108729529205203",
      "conversation_id": "2053108729529205203"
