      "created_at": "2026-05-09T13:33:22.000Z",
      "text": "One startup claims 12M tokens, 52x speed at 1M tokens and nearly 1,000x less compute.\n\nTwo AI-agent signals landed in the same week. Brett Goldstein says the next defensible layer is context, a company brain with entities, relationships, episodic memory, search and update. https://t.co/Tw8Ir2gvLs",
