      "created_at": "2026-05-09T13:09:41.000Z",
      "text": "Everyone suddenly became an “AI Agent expert” after connecting OpenAI API to Telegram.\n\nMeanwhile actual agent workflows need:\nmemory, orchestration, retries, context handling, tools, observability, and sane architecture.\n\nBut sure… your “Jarvis clone” is revolutionary.\n\n#ai",
