      "author_id": "807112444409573376",
      "created_at": "2026-05-09T09:18:31.000Z",
      "text": "为什么 Context Caching 会成为 AI Agent 时代的重要基础设施？\n现在越来越多人开始意识到：AI 真正昂贵的地方：其实不是：👉 模型本身。而是：👉 持续 inference。另一个关键 insight：👉 AI Agent systems 会产生大量重复 context。比如：👉 system prompts\n👉 memory layers\n👉 workflow https://t.co/L1ofU8Kxkc",
      "id": "2053041916380598725",
      "conversation_id": "2053041916380598725"
