      "author_id": "1199012149965676545",
      "created_at": "2026-05-09T05:41:46.000Z",
      "text": "Added memory and multi-tenancy to my AI agent this week.\nMemory: LLM summarizes old messages at 75% context usage. Recent turns stay intact. Agent forgets gracefully, not abruptly.\nMulti-tenancy: isolated prompts, knowledge, and token budgets per tenant. Three-tier",
      "id": "2052987370224619992",
      "conversation_id": "2052987370224619992"
    },
