      "author_id": "1858951559234699264",
      "created_at": "2026-05-08T21:00:09.000Z",
      "text": "My AI agent caught a pricing error in a proposal before I sent it.\n\nNot because I asked it to review pricing.\n\nBecause it had context on the client's budget from a previous conversation.\n\nThat's the real unlock — agents with memory, not just agents with tools.",
      "id": "2052856102514049431",
      "conversation_id": "2052856102514049431"
    },
