      "author_id": "1902304775539949568",
      "created_at": "2026-05-08T18:52:24.000Z",
      "text": "most ai agent failures aren't the llm being wrong. it's the agent making 40 tool calls and losing context by call 15. the hard problem is memory management not intelligence",
      "id": "2052823951961690343",
      "conversation_id": "2052823951961690343"
