      "author_id": "96586762",
      "created_at": "2026-05-08T15:59:54.000Z",
      "text": "The easiest way to create a new AI agent is to copy the main assistant and change the name.\n\nThat is also the fastest way to create a mess.\n\nSpecialized agents should not inherit broad context, broad tools, broad memory, and broad permissions by default.",
      "id": "2052780542576193582",
